{"title":"天山珍珠（图片）","authors":["林茂兰　遐晖"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山珍珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林茂兰　摄影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遐晖　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的山是这样高远偏僻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风在山下驻足，云在山边歇息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山顶有一座太阳的宫殿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳刚从这里起程，一把珍珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗落在山的怀里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了珍珠，亘古的山开始挪移"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉默中透出晶莹的生机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了草地，珍珠在静静回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满背璀璨滚动着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与太阳一同诞生的希冀"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}